{"tid":748820,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[終極篇] 何Wayne 🇭🇰 vs 何輝 🇨🇳 22:00","createTime":"2018-07-19T13:37:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T02:29:30.000Z","uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"abdf2ccb75063901a479625df325e8cc7c5e9c1f","tid":748820,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T13:37:54.000Z","msg":"《如何講世盃》Live<br />\n主持：何輝、何Wayne<br />\n日期：7月19日（周4）<br />\n直播時間：晚上十時<br />\n體蘋果Facebook直播<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh-hk.facebook.com/appledailysports/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-hk.facebook.com%2Fappledailysports%2F&d=Iv53R8qlHEix5Sbz7pAx2m6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=d1651949\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh-hk.facebook.com/appledailysports/</a>"},{"pid":"aa3e04532cc81073f39a1f2a202fcb59e10494ac","tid":748820,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T13:40:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iZjdGcRYT5w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DiZjdGcRYT5w&d=Iv53R8qlHEix5Sbz7pAx2m6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=75b20c43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iZjdGcRYT5w</a>"},{"pid":"22a7f8977dc25b7a4985ee5091c20d7a15ece478","tid":748820,"uid":59919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T13:40:50.000Z","msg":"又比人撚"},{"pid":"a8b2b275f03ab3979a13344d4e56c8b73fce2963","tid":748820,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T13:51:15.000Z","msg":"【如何講世盃Live】何輝何Wayne世盃總結 防反球隊得天下？<br />\n<br />\n世界盃完美落幕，喺呢個月入面，縱使捱眼瞓，但依然留下唔少美麗回憶，相信球迷應該收貨。正所謂人生有幾多屆世界盃，大家又要等多四年半，先可以再次投入呢種不眠不休嘅狂熱，之但係同你一齊睇波嘅人，會唔會唔同咗？你熱愛過嘅球星、熱捧過嘅球隊，又會唔會人面全非？<br />\n<br />\n大家又唔使咁快多愁善感住，事關何輝同何Wayne，今晚將會現身《如何講世盃》終極篇，同大家總結一下今屆世界盃，討論吓心水最佳11人、邊個新星最搶眼、邊場賽事最精采等等，仲會展望下屆卡塔爾世界盃。究竟未來嘅足球，會唔會係防反球隊當道？西班牙嘅tiki taka會唔會過氣？死球戰術又會唔會成為入球殺着？<br />\n今晚10點，click入《體蘋果》收睇《如何講世盃》！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/19/215108_0fccf7878c12b49c35bb389b71d8778c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F19%2F215108_0fccf7878c12b49c35bb389b71d8778c.png&h=f4e992be&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"718480f37df507acd4ed72d74042fd95bc484aca","tid":748820,"uid":53774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T13:54:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bac2639b24edfb0bf3f14054258f95e9e0be536","tid":748820,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T13:58:43.000Z","msg":"youtube開左了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d6db7d6a1587f5378557d0bfa59972e43dac072","tid":748820,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T14:00:27.000Z","msg":"kick off <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb74281cb52539974ec01a522be30deb77312dea","tid":748820,"uid":67867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T14:01:13.000Z","msg":"條傻仔又想俾何輝撚到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de00685c80d711fbb9d1085ac26fb09d7d80933c","tid":748820,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T14:03:36.000Z","msg":"兩位都同意派利是手球 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1145434eabe15024308cace0f22dc1030b2aca23","tid":748820,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T14:05:07.000Z","msg":"何sir 唔識扮識網球 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e86e74996